query:
UPDATE tables 
            SET 
                title = COALESCE($2, title),
                description = COALESCE($3, description),
                slots = COALESCE($4, slots),
                game_system_id = COALESCE($5, game_system_id),
                updated_at = NOW()
            WHERE id = $1
            RETURNING
                id,
                gm_id,
                title,
                description,
                slots,
                game_system_id,
                created_at,
                updated_at
